WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
BRAZIL-NORTHEAST COAST.
DNC 01.
1. MAN OVERBOARD FROM VESSEL IN AREA BOUND BY
   05-27.9S 034-01.0W, 05-11.8S 035-17.8W
